---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy | Wildfire Press">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="legal-page">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="last-updated">Last updated: April 8, 2026</p>

      <h2>Who We Are</h2>
      <p>Wildfire Press ("we," "us," or "our") operates the website wildfirepress.com. This policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you visit our site or interact with our services.</p>

      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <h3>Information you provide</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Email address and name</strong> when you subscribe to our newsletter or an author's mailing list</li>
        <li><strong>Contact information</strong> if you reach out to us directly</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Information collected automatically</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Usage data</strong> such as pages visited, time spent on site, and referring URLs</li>
        <li><strong>Device information</strong> such as browser type, operating system, and screen size</li>
        <li><strong>Cookies and similar technologies</strong> used for analytics and site functionality</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>To send newsletters, new release announcements, and promotional content you've opted into</li>
        <li>To improve our website and understand how visitors use it</li>
        <li>To respond to your questions or requests</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Email Marketing</h2>
      <p>We use MailerLite to manage our email lists. When you subscribe, your information is stored and processed by MailerLite in accordance with their <a href="https://www.mailerlite.com/legal/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">privacy policy</a>. You can unsubscribe at any time using the link at the bottom of any email.</p>

      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>We may use third-party services for analytics, email delivery, and hosting. These services may collect information as described in their own privacy policies. We do not sell your personal information to third parties.</p>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>Our site may use cookies to improve your browsing experience and to gather analytics data. You can control cookie settings through your browser preferences.</p>

      <h2>Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
        <li>Request correction or deletion of your data</li>
        <li>Unsubscribe from marketing emails at any time</li>
        <li>Opt out of analytics tracking via your browser settings</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>Our site is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.</p>

      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.</p>

      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at <strong>hello@wildfirepress.com</strong>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
